oshi.software.common

Class AbstractOSVersionInfoEx

  • java.lang.Object
    • oshi.software.common.AbstractOSVersionInfoEx
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, OperatingSystemVersion
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    FreeBsdOSVersionInfoEx, LinuxOSVersionInfoEx, MacOSVersionInfoEx, SolarisOSVersionInfoEx, WindowsOSVersionInfoEx

    public class AbstractOSVersionInfoEx
extends Object
implements OperatingSystemVersion
    Contains operating system version information. The information includes major and minor version numbers, a build number, a platform identifier, and descriptive text about the operating system.
